===Recordinfo options key===
*WR: World record
*OR: Olympic record
*CR: Commonwealth record
*ER: European record
*AF: African record
*AS: Asian record
*OC: Oceania record
*AM: Americas record
*<nowiki>#</nowiki>: Any records yet to be officially ratified by the relevant governing body, i.e. not yet appearing on the official records list. (Reference for all records of this type is required)
*Records not set in finals:
**h: Heats
**r: Relay 1st leg
**rh: Relay 1st leg heats
**sf: Semifinal
**b: B-final
**tt: Time-trail
**†: Intermediate split

See [[Template:Swimmingrecordlegend]] for more.

